        <updateDate>2021-08-12T19:38:29Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>PFAS Free Military Purchasing Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Defense (DOD) from procuring or purchasing specified items (e.g., cleaning products) containing a perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substance, commonly referred to as PFAS. These substances are man-made and may have adverse human health effects. A variety of products contain the compounds, such as nonstick cookware or weatherproof clothing.</p> <p>DOD may not authorize the sale of any specified item containing PFAS on DOD property, such as commissaries or online exchange shops.</p> </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
